data.description: ASSUMABLE LOAN with a rate of 3%!!!! Luxury condo unit in the vibrant Tyson's Boro neighborhood on the 21st floor. This gorgeous condo features 10 foot ceilings in the living room. Signature kitchen custom designed by Cecconi Simone, featuring Italian cabinetry and composite stone countertops, long kitchen island with waterfall edge and Bosch appliances. Porcelain Calcutta marbleized floor and tile, custom Italian vanity in the bathroom. Beautiful hardwood floors throughout. Not only do you get a beautiful condo but it also comes with furniture from Room and Board, West Elm. Ceiling fan in the living room, 65 Sony Bravia TV with Sonos Beam sound system, Alexis smart home and an Eco Bee thermostat included. There is a front load washer and dryer, a reserved garage parking spot (#68), car charging stations, a secure bicycle storage, pet spa, guest suite with hotel amenities, Amazon Hub for deliveries and returns, "The Transit Assist" that displays commuting info. SkyPark on level 9, offering lawn area with movies, central kitchen with gas grills and bar, fire pits and chairs. You'll also find the gym with cardio and weightlifting equipment, yoga studio, outdoor swimming pool.  The Verse is ideally located with immediate access to Whole Foods Market, Greensboro Metro Station, local shops and restaurants, new luxury movie theater, close to Galleria and Tyson's mall, Dulles Airport.
